# Design System Rules

## Colors (CSS Custom Properties)

All colors are defined as HSL values in `src/styles/globals.css`. Components must use Tailwind classes that reference these tokens. NEVER hardcode hex/rgb values in components.

### Brand Colors
- Primary: `bg-primary` / `text-primary` (Indigo-600, `#4F46E5`)
- Accent: `bg-accent` (Amber-500, `#F59E0B`)
- Destructive: `bg-destructive` (Red-600, `#DC2626`)
- Success: Use `text-emerald-600` / `bg-emerald-50`

### Priority Colors (Semantic)
- P1 Critical: `text-red-500` / `bg-red-50` / border `border-red-500`
- P2 High: `text-orange-500` / `bg-orange-50` / border `border-orange-500`
- P3 Medium: `text-blue-500` / `bg-blue-50` / border `border-blue-500`
- P4 Low: `text-slate-400` / `bg-slate-50` / border `border-slate-300`

### Surfaces
- Background: `bg-background` (white / slate-950 dark)
- Surface: `bg-card` (slate-50 / slate-900 dark) -- for cards, panels
- Border: `border-border` (slate-200 / slate-700 dark)

## Typography

- Font: Inter (variable)
- App body text: `text-sm` (14px) -- compact like Todoist
- Headings: `text-2xl font-bold` (H1), `text-xl font-semibold` (H2), `text-lg font-semibold` (H3)
- Caption/meta: `text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground`

## Spacing

- Card padding: `p-3` (12px)
- Panel padding: `p-4` (16px)
- List item gap: `gap-2` (8px)
- Section gap: `gap-4` (16px)

## Component Patterns

- Cards: `rounded-lg shadow-sm border` + `hover:shadow-md transition-shadow`
- Buttons: Use shadcn `<Button>` variants (default, destructive, outline, ghost)
- Inputs: Use shadcn `<Input>`, `<Textarea>`, `<Select>`
- Dialogs: Use shadcn `<Dialog>` with `shadow-lg`
- Badges/Tags: `rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium`

## Dark Mode

- Tailwind `class` strategy (`.dark` class on `<html>`)
- All component colors use semantic tokens that auto-switch
- FullCalendar CSS variables override in `.dark` scope
